## âš ï¸ Important Rules

1. **Run CLI First** - Before importing any shadcn component, ensure you've run the add command
2. **Don't Edit ui/ Directly** - Treat `components/ui/` as generated code; create wrappers instead
3. **Check components.json** - Ensure your configuration matches your project setup
4. **Update Regularly** - Run `npx shadcn@latest add <component>` to update existing components

