## ğŸš¨ Common Mistakes

| Mistake | Why It's Wrong | Correct Approach |
|---------|----------------|------------------|
| Copy-pasting from docs | Missing dependencies, wrong structure | `npx shadcn@latest add <component>` |
| Editing files in `ui/` | Changes lost on updates | Create wrapper components |
| Manual npm installs | Missing peer deps, wrong versions | CLI handles dependencies |
| Skipping `init` | Missing config, broken paths | Run `npx shadcn@latest init` first |

