## ğŸ“‹ Workflow Checklist

When adding a new shadcn component:

- [ ] Check if component is already added (`src/components/ui/`)
- [ ] Run `npx shadcn@latest add <component-name>`
- [ ] Wait for CLI to complete and install dependencies
- [ ] Import from `@/components/ui/<component>`
- [ ] Use component with appropriate variants/props
- [ ] Create wrapper if custom styling needed

